80.3	Hate_speech	Hate speech	Hate speech is, outside the law, any communication that disparages a person or a group on the basis of some characteristic such as race, color, ethnicity, gender, disability, sexual orientation, nationality, religion, or other characteristic.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/d/d5/Redacted777.jpg/100px-Redacted777.jpg
